item.title: 【Albums (lossy)】Dolby Atmos - BABYMONSTER - BABYMONS7ER (1st Mini Album) [TIDAL DOLBY ATMOS]
item.description:
BABYMONS7ER is the debut mini album by BABYMONSTER. It was released on April 1, 2024 with "Sheesh" serving as the album's title track.

"Stuck In The Middle" was pre-released on February 1, 2024.

This album marks the official debut of member Ahyeon as she had been unable to participate in the previous group activities due to health reasons.[1]

The physical album comes in eight versions: Photobook and seven individual Tag Albums.



Track list
"Monsters (Intro)" - 0:44
"Sheesh" - 2:50
"Like That" - 2:48
"Stuck In The Middle (7 ver.)" - 4:06
"Batter Up (7 ver.)" - 3:08
"Dream" - 3:03
"Stuck In The Middle (Remix)" - 3:19
